{"tid":374512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老尾隻仆街老鼠","createTime":"2017-08-25T19:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T19:57:04.000Z","uid":60695,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44b76ff3ba88fa5f5719e713157ca0a3b1572761","tid":374512,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T19:22:56.000Z","msg":"尋日發現屋企有老鼠，呀媽買左塊老鼠膠黎諗住冶佢<br />\n<br />\n我訓上格床，而家完全訓唔撚著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇耐前聽到啲聲，十成係隻老鼠出黎搵野食，聽到啲聲越搞越勁痴撚線，又有啲撞板聲咁，我諗條仆街老鼠有9成中左伏，跟住有一下好大&rdquo;撕&rdquo;一聲，心諗仆街唔係咁都走撚到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n訓喺上格床，離完望出廳，見到塊老鼠膠移撚曬位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但而家真係好撚驚，連開電筒照下望下都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac153091cbc332bb6f97c4567ae929a0d0a5cc8f","tid":374512,"uid":60695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T19:25:33.000Z","msg":"而家好似仲有d聲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409428457941c3cc89108a054c83dee62dcbe2df","tid":374512,"uid":86301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T19:28:00.000Z","msg":"加油呀樓豬"},{"pid":"5a71a73ad9cdb108d7d73412f1cccdb261cfb77e","tid":374512,"uid":38707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T19:44:00.000Z","msg":"係你床底"},{"pid":"042f5e579434bc6179543928097ae2580e348fe4","tid":374512,"uid":137731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T19:49:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99c92dfda66ac29780547b9aac8d61e96bb1b82a","tid":374512,"uid":60695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T19:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係你床底</blockquote><br />\nDLLM<im